The Relationship Between AI, ML, and Deep Learning
AI is the umbrella concept â€” making machines smart.
ML is a way to achieve AI â€” using data to learn.
Deep Learning is a type of ML â€” for more complex tasks.

| Term          | What It Means                                 | Real-World Example                   |
